- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses deep learning techniques to improve the performance of the hand pose estimation.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with a problem that is relevant to AI applications such as human-robot interaction.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with 3D hand pose estimation, which is relevant to computer graphics applications such as virtual reality and animation.
